snippet.title: God of War: Ascension Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/god-of-war/?emcid=or-1s-412983

Witness the epic launch trailer for God of War: Ascension, available exclusively for PlayStation®3 on March 12, 2013.

Description:
Vengeance is born in the fires of betrayal in this prequel to God of War.  Join Kratos as he seeks freedom, redemption, and the clarity to avenge his family.

Visit http://www.godofwar.com for more details, and like God of War on facebook.com/godofwar to stay up to date with the latest announcements.

Rated Mature: Blood and Gore, Intense Violence, Nudity, and Sexual Content
